<strong>#How much time will be taken by the RPC for QC?</strong>

At RPC, every item will be quality checked thoroughly to validate customer complaint. The RPC will take a maximum ofÂ 72Â hoursÂ to process the shipments.
<strong>#What if my item is â€˜QC failedâ€™ at RPC?</strong>

